Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:05.76,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:09.22,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:09.81,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:10.91,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and ready some towels and a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.07,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.55,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone call the doctor yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:12.56,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hikari and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.34,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:17.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.49,Main,chisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka! Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.40,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.50,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan held me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:34.45,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and then all of my lost feelings \Ncame back to me like breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:39.28,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's because my Ena is \Nshouting that it loves Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:40.42,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.31,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Just like breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:48.15,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,not only my feelings, but all sorts \Nof feelings came into my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:56.63,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan's mom loved Miuna-chan's \Ndad and left for the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:01:00.66,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san, Tsumugu-kun's grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:04.34,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-san from the candy \Nstore, Kouji-niisan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.05,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And other people who I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:10.43,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,all left for the surface for \Nthe ones they loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:14.66,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And among them was Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.88,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Ojoshi-sama was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:21.91,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What I was feeling in the shining sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.40,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,was the story that melted into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.47,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The story of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:34.04,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea God came to love Ojoshi-sama, \Neven though she was a sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.61,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and things became painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:41.27,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that before Ojoshi-sama \Nbecame a sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.55,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,she was in love with \Nsomeone on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:48.37,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he was the one \Nwho ripped them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.64,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But Ojoshi-sama never \Nblamed him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.14,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:59.25,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The more the Sea God \Nfell in love with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.49,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,the more pain he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.24,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing her cry in secret
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:07.06,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,because she was unable \Nto forget the one she loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.12,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,he decided to return \Nher to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:13.23,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But the Sea God knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:17.22,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The one that the Ojoshi-sama \Nleft behind on the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:20.40,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't bear the pain of\N losing the one he loved
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.96,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and was not of this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:30.08,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Sea God took away the \Nher ability to love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.81,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If she had those feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.21,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,she may follow in her love's foot steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.27,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,unable to bear with the \Ndespair of losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:52.67,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The calmed sea is \Nthe Ojoshi-sama's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.40,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,A peaceful heart that lost its love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.91,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and will never storm again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:01.75,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:03.63,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.19,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki! How's Manaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.55,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.77,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:21.88,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka! Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is... pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:36.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Miuna"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.50,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,the beautiful sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.48,Main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.07,Main,people,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.48,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.28,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If we force her out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,she'll end up just like Mukaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to just \Nsit here and watch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Just helplessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna was always looking at the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.11,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.89,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.52,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.62,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.64,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's better not to do anything rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.57,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see if there is any \Nchange in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.82,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like quite the ruckus \Nhas happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.58,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.20,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:07.09,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea God asked me \Nto take him to Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.31,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,For Manaka to fall in love with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.80,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wished for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.51,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to be laughing \Nthe closest to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.04,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect Manaka's smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:24.13,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who was\N the closest to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.58,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and protected me when \NI came to the surface and felt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.88,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,like I was going to be\Ncrushed by anxiety was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.95,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And yet I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.98,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't even realize your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.64,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.20,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.41,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.11,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.14,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.84,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt you really badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck would you fall \Nin love with a guy like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Manaka feels the \Nsame way about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:03.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna end up \Nlike this, it's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.24,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were able to love Akari,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.68,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,this happiness exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.30,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want her to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You were right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't love, I wouldn't be sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you have feelings for someone,\N someone else will cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Someone will be \Nsacrificed and get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what love means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.23,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,to fall in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, take it, Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,My ability to fall in \Nlove with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Take the whole damn thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:52.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And save Miuna in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.26,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan's feelings are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:16.85,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,He's crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.17,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.04,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.36,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea God is an idiot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:32.72,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God, why did you steal \Naway Ojoshi-sama's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:36.28,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the Ojoshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.52,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could tell the Sea God...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.26,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.62,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to fall in \Nlove with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.04,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.53,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.95,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.75,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shioshishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.07,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.64,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,with someone that cares so \Nmuch for me and can cry for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.26,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.27,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me this, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:12.90,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think that it's hopeless \Nor useless to love someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.37,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.65,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Falling in love with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.63,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,is not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna! Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.23,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The Ojoshi-samas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.82,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.01,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.77,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sea... God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.04,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ojoshi-sama's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,into the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.81,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.20,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.56,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,They're going into the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:09.89,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to forget him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:12.65,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,However, more than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.63,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:19.48,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,the children and my days with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:25.47,Italics,ojoshi,0000,0000,0000,,My loving heart that is within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.61,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.23,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,How unbelievable as a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.33,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.56,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You stole Ojoshi's feelings of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:43.58,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,yet you didn't even know who \Nthose feelings were directed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.18,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:50.51,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,you just now found out the truth behind \NOjoshi's feelings that melted into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's responding to the Ojoshi-sama's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.64,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a hold of Manaka \Nin place of Ojoshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:08.09,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea God's frank feelings that \Nmelted into the sea have calmed down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.65,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,and the sea is now at a lull.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:13.35,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they are not hurt, \Nthere will be no waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:17.19,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,However, though there is no sadness there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.39,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,there is no happiness either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred fire is the Sea \NGod's consciousness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.67,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.56,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred fire threw \Naway its own identity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.36,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,and carried out the duties as the god...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:35.07,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,But it must have remembered because of \NOjoshi-sama's heart that melted into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.50,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.89,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.54,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I am a scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.87,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The scale of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.92,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:47.99,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the Sea God, Ojoshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.44,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I will love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.44,Main,hkari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:16.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You scared the hell out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your hibernation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.97,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, you've gotten big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.04,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:36.14,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,A child born between a person from the \Nsurface and the sea will lose their Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.92,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,That is why with the impending \Ndanger coming to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.66,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,the people of the sea had to hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.28,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure that there were \Ndescendants to leave behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.82,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,and that there was \Na chance at a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.62,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.74,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna has Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.50,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, there is hope for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that okay, Uroko-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.20,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,It won't do any good to ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:08.08,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who woke him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.96,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go meet Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:11.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you even know \Nabout Miuna's Ena?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.66,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.64,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:25.01,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,About Miuna having Ena now, \Nand about Akira being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.02,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.14,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings also reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.62,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The heart that doesn't \Nchange for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.89,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The heart that changes with the times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.97,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,None of them are a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.32,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:07.11,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The calmed sea begins to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.20,Main,villager,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.33,Main,villager,0000,0000,0000,,It had been calm this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.25,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.41,Main,village,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out the boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.52,Main,village,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.49,Main,village,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.41,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Love is born from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.91,Main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.66,Main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.02,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hikari, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.50,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,We believed in you, our beloved friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.24,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle and kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.36,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.56,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The rough and painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:16.55,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, the sea is forever kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:27.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:32.49,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Love is like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.80,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what about worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're sturdy, Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Sturdy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sturdy as a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.89,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:58.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Manaka-san that \NI knew since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.99,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Saying welcome back is \Nmy line, Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.88,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.60,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.66,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is born from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:37.18,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oshiooshi Fishing Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.59,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Giant squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.92,Main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.66,Main,kid 2,0000,0000,0000,,Whale shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.62,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.03,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, still didn't get enough sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Here, food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So Old Man Hayakawa \Nstill hasn't woken up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.52,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,He was always a worrywort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.81,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,He probably plans to \Ncontinue hibernating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So we probably won't be able \Nto see him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:03.87,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when everyone wakes up is their own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Manaka's still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.27,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.97,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,She said she forgot something, \Nso we should head up without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:16.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's wait up top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.06,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Things same as usual \Nwith you and Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that come from all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.95,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should go on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.39,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You found out you feel the\N same way about each other after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a problem that\N there's been no progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.20,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being like Chisaki \Nfrom a little while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.32,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,The whole "I don't \Nwant to change" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, things can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:41.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But things don't have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.50,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Hii-kun is mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.06,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.26,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You came to the sea again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:04.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san was getting angry that you \Nkept coming since you were able to dive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.23,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sea's gotten pretty warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, if you come in \Ntoo often, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.59,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You still aren't used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.93,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.50,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:29.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Want a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.14,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving today, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.05,Juice,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Animals Juice\N Tangerine\NFull of Vitamins
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.50,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd come see the sea before \Nheading back to the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.65,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Won't Chii-chan be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:47.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back on breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.48,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I love the sea that you \Ncan see from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell Hikari \Nthat instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:04.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That wasn't about \NHii-kun or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.45,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.91,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Ee you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.80,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When Manaka and Tsumugu first met,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.81,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a fateful meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.33,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.33,Main,brat,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:33.96,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to the city or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.83,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is actually fated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.41,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're able to change \Neverything ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.09,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does this look okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.15,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:01.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this makes me \Nlook a little more mature...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I think if you don't \Nstand on your tip-toes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,the more Kaname-san will \Nunderstand how great you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:09.97,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.86,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I lived on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.04,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.07,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with \Nsomeone from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:15.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.30,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.27,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Heyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.94,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,I think Shiodome's gotten \Nprettier lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.18,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.83,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And the tears I shed over my first love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.45,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,melted into the kind sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.33,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.34,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:46.00,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The sea that melted everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.81,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.12,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.23,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:03.19,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, it will bring new \Nlife and new feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.10,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop by my home \Nin the sea on the way back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll be a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.81,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back to the sea if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:18.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the miso soup you make is salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about your blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:26.88,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,My mom said she'd teach me how to make\N dishes that would be healthy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:29.76,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu, were you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:37.06,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the station with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:37.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back at the end \Nof the month to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.08,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.10,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the surface world \Nthat will come some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.92,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know exactly what'll happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.37,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oshiooshi Fishing Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.16,Grocer1,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shishio and Oshishi's \N{\c&H0000FF}Cooperative Development
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.16,Grocer2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Side Dishes from\N the Sea and Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:55.20,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel that our feelings \Nwill be able to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:59.12,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:03.59,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,humans are quite interesting, \Nare they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:07.47,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Even after being hurt, \Nand having no answers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:10.89,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,They still struggle \Nand continue to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:15.45,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,And those feelings may change \Nthe great flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:19.57,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:23.73,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,So the saltflake snow has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:34.95,Episode-Title,ep title,0000,0000,0000,,Final Episode:\NThe Color of the Sea. The Color of the Earth. The Color of the Wind. The Color of Your Heart. Your Color.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:39.47,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hii-kun. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:42.37,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago at the Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:45.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,About you wanting to tell me \Nsomething after it was over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So you did remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:50.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.77,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I don't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:57.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I already know what you wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:01.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Melted into the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:03.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,melted into the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:05.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Going beyond time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings are passed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:13.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This world is filled
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:17.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,with so many shining feelings.
